ng with a Pinball Bumper, or put the chomp on them with the Venus Spy-Trap. While one trap is good, more is…evil-er. Combo your traps to banish intruders for good!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Nefarious Plots!</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700600/extras/21287b05008a553b3cca70f8d644db21.poster.avif?t=1734453187\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700600/extras/21287b05008a553b3cca70f8d644db21.webm?t=1734453187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700600/extras/21287b05008a553b3cca70f8d644db21.mp4?t=1734453187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Carry out evil schemes to further your plot to build a Doomsday Device and dominate the world! Sell the British Royal Family, Kidnap the Governor of Maine, and literally BAKE ALASKA. With hundreds of potential objectives, variety is the spice of strife.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700600/extras/b94d8851e7f472695ab3ca66f099ea11.poster.avif?t=1734453187\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700600/extras/b94d8851e7f472695ab3ca66f099ea11.webm?t=1734453187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700600/extras/b94d8851e7f472695ab3ca66f099ea11.mp4?t=1734453187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Gifs are taken from pre-release footage</i>",
